            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Realistic Driving Experience",
            "text": "<p>In manual mode, your child can take full control of the Bentley Bentayga Electric Ride-On Car, giving them a true sense of freedom on every adventure. <br/></p><p><br/>This feature encourages confidence and lets them experience the excitement of driving, all while ensuring their safety in a controlled environment. Meanwhile, the 2.4GHz parental remote control gives you peace of mind, letting you guide their ride when needed. </p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_J7U8zB": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bentley_Mulsanne_Electric_Ride-On_Car_for_Toddlers_Seat.webp",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Supportive Seat for Ultimate Comfort",
            "text": "<p>Built with a supportive seat to ensure your child’s comfort on every adventure.<br/><br/>The soft and supportive seat provides a premium feel while keeping your little driver cozy, even on longer adventures. <br/></p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_UMznCd": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bentley_Mulsanne_Electric_Ride-On_Car_for_Toddlers_Tire.webp",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Tough Tires and Excellent Suspension",
            "text": "<p>The tires features durable tires that provide superior traction and a quiet ride. </p><p><br/>Coupled with excellent rear suspension, these tires absorb bumps and vibrations, ensuring that your little one enjoys a smooth, comfortable journey. </p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_6anEEk": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bentley_Mulsanne_Electric_Ride-On_Car_for_Toddlers_Ignition.webp",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Effortless Ignition Paired with Soft, Controlled Movement",
            "text": "<p>With push-to-start ignition, your child can begin their ride instantly. The soft start function ensures smooth acceleration, preventing sudden jolts, while forward/reverse controls make navigation easy. A perfect blend of comfort and control.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_LnUXnj": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bentley_Mulsanne_Electric_Ride-On_Car_for_Toddlers_Brake.webp",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Precision Brakes for Confident Driving",
            "text": "<p>Paired with advanced safety features, this braking system delivers confident, secure driving for your little one, ensuring a safe and enjoyable ride.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_QMVnUf": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bentley_Mulsanne_Electric_Ride-On_Car_for_Toddlers_Lead_Lights.webp",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "LED Lights for a Realistic Drive",
            "text": "<p>Bright LED headlights, rear lights, and a glowing dashboard bring every ride to life. Whether cruising by day or night, these details add style, safety, and realism to your child’s driving adventure.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
