            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Longer Battery Life",
            "text": "<p>The Bentley EXP 12 Speed 6e Ride-On runs on a 12V rechargeable battery, delivering up to 2 hours of playtime per charge. <br/><br/>With high and low-speed modes, it ensures a smooth ride, while smart charging technology prevents overcharging for long-lasting performance.</p>",
